{"tid":491813,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iphone自己動手換電請教","createTime":"2017-12-07T01:25:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-07T05:56:05.000Z","uid":24962,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"1d11d7a403da42257281c6526d364ee30c8bb3d4","tid":491813,"uid":24962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T01:25:16.000Z","msg":"最近iphone冇電到倒水咁快<br />\n嘩屌<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/07/092109_053c64ec0df2a6a08f83099e49201d68.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F07%2F092109_053c64ec0df2a6a08f83099e49201d68.jpg&h=7c571421&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n得返100<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n由於過左保又唔想哂6百幾剩係換粒電<br />\n想去淘返幾舊或者好似之前有巴打話香港$110粒(疑似)原裝電<br />\n<br />\n請問有邊位淘過換過電既巴打指教一下? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eb5e339257538fead8dceb737e4f7b0b4564248","tid":491813,"uid":6250,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T01:26:34.000Z","msg":"咩app黎"},{"pid":"1abb1255e68d6a17907c3c07efceac86aae5bbc0","tid":491813,"uid":9232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T01:28:03.000Z","msg":"街外唔會有原裝新電，只有拆機二手電<br />\n自己淘試下換啦，youtube大把教學"},{"pid":"ef5f9c997202073b96eb32cbfe4ed5c3420a544e","tid":491813,"uid":102738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T01:28:28.000Z","msg":"我都想學"},{"pid":"0ba885cc5cd21a0888bfd0ea2e8671b7c23fba42","tid":491813,"uid":3344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T01:29:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩app黎</blockquote><br />\nbattery life"},{"pid":"81681ff0478db092591905486badbbd44be320b0","tid":491813,"uid":24962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T01:29:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩